此高架車站設有兩個[[側式月台|側式月台]]和三條軌道。中央軌道不營運。

2014年7月5日至2015年4月27日，作為佩勒姆線五個車站的1.09億美元重建計劃<ref name="reopening42715">{{cite press release|title=Zerega Av and Buhre Av 6 Stations To Reopen After Renewal Project|url=http://www.mta.info/news-zerega-av-buhre-ave-pelham-line-6/2015/04/24/zerega-av-and-buhre-av-6-stations-reopen-after|publisher=Metropolitan Transportation Authority|accessdate=April 26, 2015|date=April 24, 2015|archive-date=2016-07-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160728225836/http://www.mta.info/news-zerega-av-buhre-ave-pelham-line-6/2015/04/24/zerega-av-and-buhre-av-6-stations-reopen-after|dead-url=no}}</ref>，此站與[[布雷爾大道車站_(IRT佩勒姆線)|布雷爾大道車站]]一同關閉進行車站翻新工程<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.mta.info/press-release/nyc-transit/zerega-avenue-and-buhre-avenue-6-line-stations-close-seven-months-renewal|title=MTA - Press Release - NYC Transit - Zerega Avenue and Buhre Avenue 6 Line Stations to Close  for Seven Months for Renewal|publisher=|accessdate=11 April 2016|archive-date=2016-08-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160821133350/http://www.mta.info/press-release/nyc-transit/zerega-avenue-and-buhre-avenue-6-line-stations-close-seven-months-renewal|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://web.mta.info/nyct/service/planned_servChanges_6trains.htm|title=mta.info - Service Notice|publisher=|accessdate=11 April 2016|archive-date=2016-04-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160420174319/http://web.mta.info/nyct/service/planned_servChanges_6trains.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。
